Install-Module PnP.PowerShell
Connect-PnPOnline -Url https:/tenant.sharepoint.com/sites/site -UseWebLogin
Get-PnPSearchSettings
Set-PnPSearchSettings -SearchScope 2
Get-PnPSearchSettings





0 = default, let SharePoint decide
1 = All sites in the organization
2 = All sites in this Hub
3 = Just this site 
